<navigation-bar title="晚自习小程序" back="{{false}}" color="white" background="transparent"></navigation-bar>

<view class="gateway-page">
  <view class="gateway-head">
    <text class="gateway-kicker">Role Gateway</text>
    <text class="gateway-title">先看页面骨架</text>
    <text class="gateway-subtitle">我们先把教师端和家长端的小样搭起来，后面再接真实登录和后端。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="gateway-card" bindtap="goTeacher">
    <text class="gateway-card-tag">教师端</text>
    <text class="gateway-card-title">晚自习录入工作台</text>
    <text class="gateway-card-copy">学生侧边栏、四维评分、课堂反馈、作业照片上传。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="gateway-card" bindtap="goParent">
    <text class="gateway-card-tag">家长端</text>
    <text class="gateway-card-title">今日情况 + 记录回看</text>
    <text class="gateway-card-copy">首页看当天记录，记录页看日历，底部三栏结构保留。</text>
  </view>
</view>
